| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5063 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ef2a2299-6c21-5b91-abd9-70f580d4f574"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
